premise_source_doc_sentence: Nasir Bin Olu Dara Jones  (  -LSB- nɑːˈsɪər -RSB- born September 14 , 1973  )  , better known by his stage name Nas -LSB- ˈnɑːz -RSB- , is an American rapper , record producer , actor , and entrepreneur .

After another New York City rapper , Jay-Z , attacked Nas in his album The Blueprint , Nas released Stillmatic in 2001 with a track responding to Jay-Z 's attack along with two singles that once again made the top ten spots of the Billboard rap chart , `` Got Ur Self A. .
